{"tid":1794463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別","createTime":"2019-12-23T06:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:54:01.000Z","uid":163704,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8af40cdefdf07338a4494d822cc2bd2a9f4fe15b","tid":1794463,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"網站內的搜尋器已經完成，而家會進行增設那些分類的調查。請大家留言話我地知希望會有那些分類。<br />\n暫時我地知道有用戶感興趣的分類<br />\n1, 香港的失蹤人口<br />\n2, 香港的被捕人士 (呢款資料比較敏感)<br />\n3, 香港的黃藍食店 (市面上已經有數款網頁/應用程式)<br />\n4, 香港的黃藍非食店<br />\n5, 香港警暴濫權極合 (我知道已經有人做)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factvote.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factvote.com&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=09fe64ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factvote.com</a>"},{"pid":"8f4b319d08aa577d38dbf46e9a9dff6ecd13a887","tid":1794463,"uid":163704,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"Factvote係一個以&lsquo;尋找事件真相為目的&rsquo;的網頁。你可以為一件事件提出全部或部分一手或二手證據。再由其他人核實或提出你未知的證據而令事件能全面呈現出來。<br />\n<br />\n我地需要大家去創建唔同事件(只有一個證據都可以，會有人幫大家提供其他證據)，同時亦需要大家提供證據去幫我地完善每一個事件。<br />\n<br />\n要一個人每一樣野由零開始做起FC係唔可能。但大家只要做多少少，每人提供自己見過的證據。咁只要睇一個post就可以自己判斷，仲做埋fact check。呢個係我地寫呢個網站的原因。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位提供意見<br />\ninfo@factvote.com<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FactVote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFactVote&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=a98a323f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FactVote</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/factvotedotcom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffactvotedotcom&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=ab149fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/factvotedotcom</a>"},{"pid":"0124cf8ef8ccdcfed0666d06083e0478bd76bec4","tid":1794463,"uid":57634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12